      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Hey there! I am honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in absolute pristine condition\u2014seriously, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied it since day one, kept it garage-stored, and there\u2019s not a single scratch or dent to be found. It drives like a dream and is ready for its next adventure. You really won\u2019t find another one this clean! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to chat more about it and get you behind the wheel!",
