      "description": "Offering an exceptional E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54 naturally aspirated 3.2L inline-six. This specimen boasts a linear power delivery and razor-sharp throttle response thanks to its individual throttle bodies. All critical maintenance has been proactively addressed: the double-VANOS system has been overhauled, rod bearings replaced with high-performance treated shells, and the rear subframe has been reinforced to ensure structural integrity under high lateral loads. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission shifts with mechanical precision, paired with a limited-slip M-Differential. The suspension geometry remains true, and the chassis is free of any fatigue or corrosion. A true purist's example preserved in its factory configuration.",
